                                        <div class="panel-body editor-content">
                                            <p>For every 1 hour of learning you get 1 PDU. This course typically comprises 16 hours classroom training.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="panel panel-default">
                                    <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading-faq-2">
                                        <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq-accordion" href="#faq-2" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="faq-2"> Is there an eligibility criteria for attending this course? </a> </h4>
